### Get available vehicles
GET http://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/logistics/Vehicles?$filter=status eq 'Available'

### Get shipments with status InTransit
GET http://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments?$filter=status eq 'InTransit'

### Get all shipments for a specific customer
GET http://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments?$filter=customer_ID eq 'C001'

### Create a new shipment booking
POST http://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ID": "S001",
  "customer_ID": "C001",
  "sourceCity": "Hyderabad",
  "destinationCity": "Bangalore",
  "status": "Booked"
}

### Update shipment status to Delivered
PATCH http://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments('S001')
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Delivered",
  "deliveredAt": "2026-06-01T10:00:00Z"
}

### Get routes between two cities
GET http://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/logistics/Routes?$filter=sourceCity eq 'Hyderabad' and destinationCity eq 'Bangalore'

### Get drivers sorted by rating descending
GET http://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/logistics/Drivers?$orderby=rating desc